---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Departures — Building Line Relaxations" description="Departure applications: building line relaxations, height, coverage and parking departures. Town planners Cape Town.">
<section class="min-h-[50vh] flex items-center"><div class="wrap pt-28 pb-16"><span class="tag mb-10">Services · Departures</span><h1 class="mb-6">Departure <span class="text-accent">applications</span></h1><p class="text-text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-lg">Building line relaxations, height departures, coverage variations, and parking requirement reductions.</p></div></section>
<div class="wrap pb-24"><div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-border-subtle">
<div class="bg-bg p-8"><h3 class="mb-2">Building line</h3><p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Reduce street and lateral building lines. Build closer to boundaries when the zoning scheme is too restrictive.</p></div>
<div class="bg-bg p-8"><h3 class="mb-2">Height</h3><p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Exceed height limits for architectural features, multi-storey designs, or sloped sites.</p></div>
<div class="bg-bg p-8"><h3 class="mb-2">Coverage</h3><p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Increase site coverage allowances. Essential for maximising building footprint on small erven.</p></div>
<div class="bg-bg p-8"><h3 class="mb-2">Parking</h3><p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Reduce on-site parking requirements. Critical for small sites and urban infill projects.</p></div>
<div class="bg-bg p-8"><h3 class="mb-2">Architects</h3><p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Your design exceeds a standard — we justify the departure to the municipality so you can build.</p></div>
<div class="bg-bg p-8"><h3 class="mb-2">Property owners</h3><p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Need more space? A departure can let you build what the zoning scheme would otherwise block.</p></div>
</div></div>
<section class="py-32 text-center border-t border-border-subtle"><div class="narrow"><h2 class="mb-6">Need a <span class="text-accent">departure</span>?</h2><p class="text-text-muted text-lg mb-10">Free assessment of your building plans against zoning requirements.</p><a href="/contact/" class="btn-primary text-base px-8 py-4">Get Your Free Consultation</a></div></section>
</BaseLayout>